"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-paris-2024-2024-0730-1462692-paris-2024-darragh-gutted-after-olympic-debut-loss\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Rachael Darragh said she was left gutted after narrowly losing out to Switzerland's Jenjira Stadelmann on her Olympic Games debut.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Darragh\", \"score\": 0.9999995429585532, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rachael Darragh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Darragh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Darragh\"}, {\"begin\": 70, \"end\": 81, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9993308894283469, \"rank\": 0.0005186814561566985, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Donegal native had match point in the second set, after winning the first 21-13.\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donegal_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9752039672968256, \"rank\": 0.025426266029828302, \"text\": \"Donegal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donegal_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donegal_GAA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Stadelmann, a European Games bronze medallist, survived before going on to win the set 24-22.\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 240, \"end\": 254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\", \"score\": 0.9962199761898994, \"rank\": 0.0037582534966580134, \"text\": \"European Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew I was an underdog going into that game, she's a European Games bronze medallist, I knew I could throw everything at it and completely go for it,\\\" Darragh told RT\\u00c9 Sport.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\", \"score\": 0.9962199761898994, \"rank\": 0.0037582534966580134, \"text\": \"European Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had my chances in the second set, I had a set point there and I am really gutted I did not take that chance, but I am also very proud of my performance,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stadelmann showed her experience in the final set and was able to overcome Darragh 21-15 to secure her first win of Group L.    'I had my chances in the second set' - Rachael Darragh gutted by narrow loss to Switzerland's Jenjira Stadelmann after a deciding set#RTESport#Paris2024\\ud83d\\udcf1Updateshttps://t.co/01ShZjM17C\\ud83d\\udcfaWatchhttps://t.co/XnOP6grnB7pic.twitter.com/TQj5oiZA0Z    Darragh said: \\\"I feel, especially in the third set, I had a bit of a rhythm after the break but she used that experience and slowed it down, and really took advantage.\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9993308894283469, \"rank\": 0.0005186814561566985, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It kind of threw me a bit of the end, a lot of silly mistakes, unforced errors that I will be replaying in my head all evening, but she's a great player and well done to her today.\\\"\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Darragh faces a much more difficult task tomorrow afternoon when she will go head-to-head with 2016 Olympic champion Carolina Marin from Spain.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolina_Mar\\u00edn\", \"score\": 0.9999990899400066, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carolina Marin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolina_Mar\\u00edn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolina_Mar\\u00edn\"}, {\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999989582193818, \"rank\": 1.0412143053561793e-06, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marin dispatched of Stadelmann by two sets to nil on Sunday in their opening group game.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's the Olympic champion from Rio, I can completely go at that again and just try give my best performance like I did today,\\\" Darragh said.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1662, \"end\": 1665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9760859491203243, \"rank\": 0.024499943657299243, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am looking forward to it, but it's a whole new step up, Olympic champion, she's here to win gold,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851268295, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 1949, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999975495076459, \"rank\": 2.4465873111852363e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1990, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Images Courtesy of Getty Images.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2077, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9978316783628383, \"rank\": 0.0016881680213185622, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wiki